Warning sign: Inventory builds
Sweet spot: Margin expansion

INDUSTRIALS:
Best quarters: Q2, Q3
Worst quarter: Q1
Key metric: Book-to-bill ratio
Warning sign: Order declines
Sweet spot: Infrastructure spend
