â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•
Official vs Whisper Spread:
<5% spread:     Normal beat needed
5-10% spread:   Big beat needed
>10% spread:    Priced for perfection
Negative spread: Surprise potential

Where to Find Whispers:
- Earnings Whispers website
- Option flow analysis
- Analyst preview notes
- Social media sentiment
- Historical beat rates

How to Trade Whispers:
Whisper too high â†’ Avoid or short
Whisper = Official â†’ Straight play
Whisper too low â†’ Hidden opportunity
