The Guidance Game
INTERPRETING GUIDANCE:
â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•
GUIDANCE SCENARIOS:

"Conservative" Guide:
- Below street expectations
- Management history of beating
- Stock drops 5-10%
ACTION: Buy the dip
Success rate: 71%

"In-Line" Guide:
- Meets expectations exactly
- No upside surprise
- Stock flat to down 2%
ACTION: Hold if owned, don't buy
Success rate: 55%

"Beat and Raise":
- Above street expectations
- Confidence in trajectory
- Stock up 5-15%
ACTION: Buy/add immediately
Success rate: 78%

"Kitchen Sink" Guide:
- Massive reduction
- New CEO cleaning house
- Stock craters 20%+
ACTION: Wait 2 quarters
Success rate: 45%
